    "long_instructions": "## Refining and Editing Chat\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to revise and improve the content you generated earlier.\r\n\r\nFocus on making your final product clearer, catchier, or more creative—based on your assigned role.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to revise or upgrade the draft you created in the last stage.\r\n    - Ask AI to make it shorter, stronger, funnier, more persuasive, or more student-friendly.\r\n    - ell AI what you like or want to change.\r\n2. In your Activity Guide under Stage 3: Generating Content, write:\r\n\t- The question or prompt you gave to AI\r\n\t- A summary of what the AI told you\r\n3. Want better results? Give AI feedback on what didn’t work in the first version and ask for a new take.",
